library(ggplot2)

data("example_datasets")

ggplot(example_datasets$cars, aes(x = mpg, fill = cyl,colour = cyl)) +
  geom_density(alpha = 0.75) +
  scale_fill_inrae() +
  scale_color_inrae() +
  labs(fill = "Cylinders", colour = "Cylinders", x = "MPG", y = "Density") +
  theme_inrae()
